{"title":"老鞋匠印象","authors":["晨光"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":7,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老鞋匠印象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只占据一个小小的角落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花镜与太阳一起升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑眯眯地检阅脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俨然是都市的皇帝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步乱乱纷纷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世尘扑朔迷离"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急步而来闲步而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄步而来信步而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹豫而来坦然而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会从散着酒香的话语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里得到满意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——鞋，这东西爱坏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人总是要走路呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路低洼不平弯弯曲曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后仔细阅读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一页行路人的日记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该粘牢的，用一抹严厉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该缝合的，牵一线思绪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锤与鞋模的碎语中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲打出几句晓白的哲理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶尔闲下来的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃香烟点燃回忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开身边发黑的木箱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清点藏了半个世纪的鞋的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞋匠的墓志铭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路上的足迹"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}